result.name: school-catchment-areas-northumberland
result.notes:
This information is published by the Northumberland County Council to inform parent/carers of their 'catchment school' for the purposes of school admissions.

These spatial areas show the catchment area for a property by its location. If you're buying a house and will be relying on this information for applying for a school place, please confirm the catchment area with us first.

RC voluntary aided schools do not have defined catchment areas. For places at RC schools apply to the County Council's  School Admissions Team for information and applications.
result.title: School Catchment areas Northumberland
